Intermediate HSSE Advisor (Temp Position)
Intermediate HSSE Advisor (Temp Position)

NSB Omega is searching for an Intermediate HSSE Advisor for our Client in St. john's, NL.

Assignment Description

Job Purpose:



 To ensure all elements of the Project’s HSSE Plan are communicated and implemented in accordance with regulatory, corporate and contract requirements.




 

Accountabilities:

 



·       Support multiple projects throughout the Life Cycle Canada organization;

·       Liaise with internal and external stakeholders to form relationships and deliver value for our clients;

·       Develop Project HSSE Plans and other contractual HSSE deliverables;

·       Participate in and ensure that site HSSE protocols are effectively carried out (ie: risk assessments, toolbox talks, orientations, site inspections, regular safety meetings, etc.);

·       Identify risks and hazards associated with work activities and facilities and confirm that appropriate controls are in place to remove or reduce the risk to acceptable levels;

·       Visit operational sites and work locations, both onshore and offshore to promote two-way engagement and visible leadership;

·       Promote Aker Solutions HSSE strategy, goals, KPIs and activity plans;

